@startuml sequence_enable_presentation
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Presentation Mode - Admin Enable Flow

actor Admin
participant "RaffleEditForm" as Form
participant "api.ts" as API
participant "Express API" as Server
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

actor Visitor
participant "DrawPage" as DP
participant "ThemeRenderer" as TR

== Admin enables presentation mode ==

Admin -> Form: Toggles presentation mode ON
Form -> API: updateRaffle(id, { presentationMode: true })
API -> Server: PUT /api/admin/raffles/:id
Server -> DB: UPDATE raffle SET\npresentationMode=true
DB --> Server: OK
Server --> API: Updated raffle
API --> Form: Success

== Public page renders with presentation mode ==

Visitor -> DP: Opens draw page
DP -> API: getActiveRaffle()
API -> Server: GET /api/public/active-raffle
Server -> DB: SELECT raffle
DB --> Server: { presentationMode: true, ... }
Server --> API: ActiveRafflePublic
API --> DP: { presentationMode: true }

DP -> TR: theme="cosmic",\npresentationMode=true
TR -> TR: Apply flat CSS overrides:\nbg=#000, no shadows,\nborder-2, larger text
DP --> Visitor: High-contrast flat UI

@enduml
